## Retry payment method

> Sample Request

```json
{
  "apiKey": "<%= config.auth %>",
  "paymentMethodId": "566595c8ce88ccec69328566"
}
```

> 200 Response

```json
{
  "success": true
}
```

> 400 Response

```json
{
  "message": "No payment method found by that ID."
}
```

Retry a `declined` payment method on file for bill payments.

### HTTP Request

`POST <%= config.host %>/payment/retry`

### Post Parameters

Param | Description
----- | -----------
`paymentMethodId` | Payment method ID.

### Returns

Returns a `200` status code if the payment method was set to retry. Returns an error otherwise.